    "id": "3191",
    "title": "Privacy Policy",
    "slug": "privacy-policy",
    "link": "https://worldinmaking.com/privacy-policy/",
    "pubDate": "Wed, 16 Jul 2025 01:17:28 +0000",
    "postDate": "2025-07-16 01:17:28",
    "author": "worldinmaking",
    "content": "<strong>privacy policy</strong> <strong>effective date:</strong> february 22, 2025 <strong>last updated:</strong> february 22, 2025\n\n \n\nwelcome to <strong>worldinmaking.com</strong> (\"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\"). we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal information. this privacy policy explains how we handle your data when you visit our website and use our services.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. information we collect</strong></h3>\n \n\nwe may collect the following types of information:\n\n \n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1.1. information you provide to us</strong></h4>\n \n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n \t<li><strong>account information:</strong> if you sign up for any services, newsletters, or participate in discussions, you may provide us with your name, email address, and other contact details.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>user submissions:</strong> if you interact with our ai-powered tools or submit content, we may collect the data you provide to personalize your experience.</li>\n</ul>\n \n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1.2. automatically collected information</strong></h4>\n \n\nwhen you visit our website, we may automatically collect certain information, including:\n\n \n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n \t<li><strong>log data:</strong> ip address, browser type, pages visited, time spent on pages, and referral sources.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>cookies and tracking technologies:</strong> we use cookies and similar technologies to enhance user experience and collect analytics data. you can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.</li>\n</ul>\n \n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1.3. third-party data collection</strong></h4>\n \n\nwe may use third-party services such as google analytics, google adsense, or other advertising networks, which may collect data through cookies and tracking technologies. these services help us analyze visitor interactions and improve our offerings.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. how we use your information</strong></h3>\n \n\nwe use the collected information for the following purposes:\n\n \n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n \t<li>to provide, operate, and improve our website and services.</li>\n \n \t<li>to personalize content and recommend relevant materials.</li>\n \n \t<li>to monitor and analyze website performance and trends.</li>\n \n \t<li>to manage advertisements and affiliate partnerships.</li>\n \n \t<li>to communicate with users regarding updates, promotions, or inquiries.</li>\n \n \t<li>to ensure website security and prevent fraud or unauthorized activities.</li>\n</ul>\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. how we share your information</strong></h3>\n \n\nwe do not sell or rent your personal data. however, we may share information in the following situations:\n\n \n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n \t<li><strong>service providers:</strong> third-party companies that assist us in analytics, hosting, and advertising.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>legal requirements:</strong> if required by law or to protect our rights and users.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>business transfers:</strong> in the event of a merger, acquisition, or business restructuring.</li>\n</ul>\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. your data rights and choices</strong></h3>\n \n\nyou have the following rights regarding your personal data:\n\n \n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n \t<li><strong>access and correction:</strong> you can request access to or correction of your personal information.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>opt-out of tracking:</strong> you can disable cookies in your browser settings.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>email communications:</strong> you can unsubscribe from our emails at any time.</li>\n \n \t<li><strong>do not sell my data:</strong> while we do not sell user data, you may opt out of targeted advertising by adjusting your preferences.</li>\n</ul>\n \n\nfor any data-related requests, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:mustafadursunkaya@worldinmaking.com\">mustafadursunkaya@worldinmaking.com</a>.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. security measures</strong></h3>\n \n\nwe implement reasonable security measures to protect your information. however, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection against unauthorized access.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>6. third-party links</strong></h3>\n \n\nour website may contain links to third-party sites. we are not responsible for their privacy practices, and we encourage users to review their policies before providing any personal data.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>7. children’s privacy</strong></h3>\n \n\nworldinmaking.com is not intended for children under the age of 13. we do not knowingly collect data from minors. if you believe a child has provided personal data, please contact us for removal.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>8. changes to this privacy policy</strong></h3>\n \n\nwe may update this privacy policy from time to time. changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage users to review it periodically.\n\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>9. contact information</strong></h3>\n \n\nif you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can contact us at:\n\n \n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n \t<li><strong>email:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:mustafadursunkaya@worldinmaking.com\">mustafadursunkaya@worldinmaking.com</a></li>\n \n \t<li><strong>website:</strong> <a href=\"https://worldinmaking.com/\">worldinmaking.com</a></li>\n</ul>\n \n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n \n\nby using <strong>worldinmaking.com</strong>, you agree to this privacy policy and the collection and use of information as described above.",
